Package: epiAneufinder
Type: Package
Title: Calling copy numbers from scATAC-seq data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Akshaya Ramakrishnan
Maintainer: The package maintainer <akshaya4r@gmail.com>
Description: Package to detect breakpoints and assign somies to scATAC-seq data.
    Also supports other single cell sequencing data.
